Install:

gem install bundler
gem bundle


Configure:

Sign up for a free account at https://rpxnow.com/

Create a new application

Copy chirp.conf.example to chirp.conf

Update chirp.conf with RPX information


Run:

./bin/rackup config.ru


Use:

Navigate to http://localhost:9292

Sign in with an OpenID account

Post messages

Follow (follow nickname)

Direct message (dm nickname message) <- No @ symbol